Towards the end of the Gothic war as the Imperial forces gained the upper hand, a new class of Chaos Battleship began to be seen. The first of which named the Siege Breaker smashed through a Imperial blockade at a warp jump point close to Bhein Morr scattering the Imperials and allowing a sizable force of damaged cruisers and destroyers of the enemy to escape into the warp.

Edited as the Port weapon batteries were inverted and wouldnt print correctly. Corrected size, now measures the same length as the other Battleships.

Please download again

Well the Big bad Warmaster needs a Big bad ship, doesn't come much bigger than this measuring 20cm in length, she is a beast. The Vengeful Spirit will make the enemies of Chaos weep. You will need a large printer for this, my Mars 2 Pro just about holds the model when split in two but to be honest to do this model justice it needs to be printed as a whole. Supports are a must especially on her stern area which will fail unless there are enough. Rules for this ship can be found online.
Enjoy her in your games
